						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Drag wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">But yeah, is there any more of an efficient way to update a column of attribute data than to just reset $2006 for each write? (by resetting, I mean manually incrementing the address by $08, and rewriting the incremented value)</div>
